RuPauls Drag race season 7

Episode One: Born Naked

March 2, 2015

At the beginning of the episode, all 14 of the queens are introduced, unlike last season where half of the queens were introduced in week one, while the other half was introduced in week two. This weeks mini-challenge was to strut the runway in one outfit from their spring collection, and one outfit from their fall collection, sponsored by D-koye, the product, hair care. There was no mini-challenge winner this week, as the looks would be reviewed on the main stage elimination day. This weeks main challenge was to create a resort-wear look that tears away to reveal a nude illusion
